  "description": "Comprehensive reference for industrial acid and base production covering sulfuric acid (lead chamber and contact processes), hydrochloric acid (Leblanc byproduct, direct synthesis), nitric acid (saltpeter and Ostwald), caustic soda (lime-soda and electrolytic), soda ash (Leblanc and Solvay), hydrofluoric acid, phosphoric acid, and acid-base safety. Supplements the individual acid and alkali capability articles with cross-referenced process details and bootstrap sequencing.",
